snippet.title: Glory of Generals intro.
snippet.description:
iOS version link: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/glory-of-generals/id605634718?ls=1&mt=8
Android version link : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.easytech.gogh
Mac version link: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/glory-of-generals/id635824112?mt=12    
Commander！ 
Over 60 campaigns in 4 battlefields of World War II are waiting for your challenge. 
102 world famous generals will participate in this war with you. 
Over 300 real and rich terrains will influence your strategies.

Notice, Glory of Generals will not support older than iOS 4.3. if your device
system is 4.21 , Please upgrade your system. Thanks!

Dear player:
The newest version of Glory of Generals has been adapted to iPhone X ! Welcome our players to download and play at Apple Store !
